snippet.title: Star Revenge 3.5 - F3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Oh hey, finally figured out what prevented me from not making trailers anymore... well, I didn't really like to make them to begin with, but for F3 I decided to make one anyway.

Since I only have to work next week for 3 days only and got 3 weeks off then, you can probably expect a lot more streams in that time, I wanna get stuff done (no, I propably won't get the whole hack done in that time, I don't have any plans/layouts for course 13 - 15 yet)

Full F3: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HOrFk7iLADM
